dct_title_s: Map of Ohio and selected parts of Michigan
dct_alternative_sm: Map of Ohio and the settled parts of Michigan, 1832 / engraved by J.H. Young.
dct_description_sm: 1 map : hand col., mounted on muslin ; 48 x 32 cm
Also shows parts of Indiana, Kentucy, Virginai, Pennsylvania, and Ontario.
Includes "Profile of the Ohio and Erie Canal."
